Package: Stock
Type: Package
Title: Statistical tools for analyzing stocks and portfolios
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-05-28
Author: Bianchi Federico, Corti Matteo, Giay Simone, Passano Andreas
Maintainer: <andreaspassano@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows the user to Download data directly from Yahoo finance. It offers tools to analyze and visualize the stocks prices and returns in order to gain a deeper statistical understanding. The user has also the possibility to form a portfolio of stocks in which to run the same analysis and test different back-testing strategies.
License: CC BY
Imports:
    TTR,
    quantmod,
    quadprog,
    ggplot2,
    shiny,
    shinydashboard,
    DT, 
    shinyWidgets
Depends:
    ggplot2,
    shiny,
    shinydashboard,
    DT, 
    shinyWidgets